title: Brunswick Dye Sub Shoe Covers
features: KEEPING YOUR KICKS CLEAN AND DRY: The Dye Sub Shoe Covers will protect your bowling shoes from the elements, giving you the confidence to step on the approach every time after removal.
EZ ON, EZ OFF: The Dye-Sub Shoe Covers go on and off your shoes with ease thanks to the Dye-Sub nylon material. You don't have to fight getting them on and off when not on the lanes!
STORES EASILY: The Dye-Sub Shoe Covers tuck easily into your bowling bag when not in use, leaving plenty of room for your other accessories!
CONTAINS A PAIR: Each order of Dye Sub Shoe Covers contains one pair of shoe covers, one for each foot!
BUY WITH CONFIDENCE: The Dye-Sub Shoe Covers carry a 1-year limited manufacturer's warranty.
